         <othermeta name="title" content="To set Field Dependencies"/>
         <othermeta name="shortdesc"
                    content="Procedure for configuring field dependencies for Guidance Types on relevant Salesforce objects so that Deal Guidance displays context-appropriate fields and options."/>
         <othermeta name="language" content="en-GB"/>
         <othermeta name="version" content="1.0.0"/>
         <othermeta name="docStage" content="approved"/>
         <othermeta name="access.role" content="internal"/>
         <othermeta name="data.classification" content="non-sensitive"/>
         <othermeta name="retention.policy" content="standard-36m"/>
         <othermeta name="entities"
                    content="guidance-types;salesforce-objects;picklist-fields;field-dependency-matrix;business-objects;configuration-records"/>
         <othermeta name="taxonomy"
                    content="domain:revenue-operations;usecase:documentation-access;industry:revenue-lifecycle-management"/>
         <othermeta name="tags"
                    content="field-dependencies,guidance-types,salesforce,configuration,validation,deploy"/>
         <othermeta name="usecase"
                    content="configuration-of-field-dependencies-for-deal-guidance"/>
      </metadata>
   </prolog>
   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>App Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Objects</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Deal Guidance Dimension Set</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Guidance Type</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the <uicontrol>Field Dependencies</uicontrol> section click
                  <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>For <uicontrol>Controlling Field</uicontrol> select <i>Guidance Type</i> and for <uicontrol>Dependent Field</uicontrol> select <i>Business Object</i> and click <uicontrol>Continue</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>For <uicontrol>Deal Level</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Line Level</uicontrol> include the following:</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <table>
                     <tgroup cols="2">
                        <colspec colname="col1"/>
                        <colspec colname="col2"/>
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>
                                    <i>
                                       <uicontrol>Deal Level</uicontrol>
                                    </i>
                                 </p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>
                                    <ul>
                                       <li>
                                          <i>Opportunity</i>
                                       </li>
                                       <li>
                                          <i> Apttus__APTS_Agreement__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                       <li>
                                          <i>Apttus_DealMgr__Deal__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                       <li>
                                          <i>Apttus_Config2__ProductConfiguration__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                    </ul>
                                 </p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>
                                    <i>
                                       <uicontrol>Line Level</uicontrol>
                                    </i>
                                 </p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>
                                    <ul>
                                       <li>
                                          <i>Apttus__AgreementLineItem__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                       <li>
                                          <i>Apttus_DealMgr__DealLineItem__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                       <li>
                                          <i> Apttus_Config2__LineItem__c</i>
                                       </li>
                                    </ul>
                                 </p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
               <fig id="fig_g1h_dg3_rcc">
                  <image height="195"
                         placement="break"
                         width="600"
                         href="../attachments/195691317/195691315.png"
                         id="image_h1h_dg3_rcc"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. When you create a <uicontrol>Deal Guidance Dimension Set</uicontrol>, the appropriate deal and line level values will be displayed.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
